</p></entry><entry colname="col4" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">LABEL, KEEP PBA-DRC
</p></entry><entry colname="col5" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "/><entry colname="col6" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "/><entry colname="col7" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "/></row></tbody></tgroup></table></section><section id="GUID-BB3176D5-4D6C-4F72-9385-B00703DA334C" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Summary</title><p class="- topic/p ">
</p><p class="- topic/p ">Swapping controllers with DRC boards on the Colorado will result in complications. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">To mitigate these follow-up problems, a warning label has been created to alert technicians during the replacement
</p><p class="- topic/p ">process to NOT swap the DRC board and the controller with another system.
</p></section><section id="GUID-234D70A5-41EC-40E2-9E43-4217D346F540" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">1 Reason</title><p class="- topic/p ">
</p><p class="- topic/p ">Swapping controllers alongside DRC boards can have significant repercussions. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">It may lead to duplicated or lost serial numbers and corruption of machine data. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">Rectifying such issues often demands substantial time, effort, and support from headquarters. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">To mitigate this risk, a warning sticker has been developed.
</p></section><section id="GUID-1AA9E77D-DF8C-4C64-B211-D49454D1F323" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">2 Description</title><p class="- topic/p ">
</p><p class="- topic/p ">The following warning label has been designed for attachment to the embedded controller box. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">In the factory, this label is affixed to new systems starting from serial number 990400596 onwards. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">For the existing Colorado field population, we strongly recommend adding this sticker during a next visit.
</p><fig id="GUID-E2648943-A251-4C5C-9B00-AC46A69977F3" class="- topic/fig "><title class="- topic/title ">3 Instruction</title><image href="GUID-4956840C-B323-43EC-BA2C-1943C94F96BC-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-4956840C-B323-43EC-BA2C-1943C94F96BC-low.png"/></fig></section><section id="GUID-EE24A29A-162B-4042-B8B3-7150B5D93B80" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">3 Instruction</title><p class="- topic/p ">Please attach the label on the mounting plate of the C14 Embedded Controller as indicated below:
</p><fig id="GUID-A1045A87-EBA5-44C8-88AE-992ABCB8A4F6" class="- topic/fig "><title class="- topic/title "/><image href="GUID-1EB38B37-D55E-4DBD-9042-10755EB4A12D-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-1EB38B37-D55E-4DBD-9042-10755EB4A12D-low.png"/></fig><fig id="GUID-783C52D0-398F-4B2B-BBCA-8F6F38A7E42B" class="- topic/fig "><title class="- topic/title "/><image href="GUID-66C8AC9B-6A2E-42FC-A200-B7D48B0A0097-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-66C8AC9B-6A2E-42FC-A200-B7D48B0A0097-low.png"/></fig></section><section id="GUID-BE49119F-FCF4-415F-9EAC-3F7CB8C56731" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">4 Registration</title><p class="- topic/p ">
